      <h1>Ops Runbook — Quirk AI (Pilot)</h1>
      <p class="sub">Start/stop, logs, TLS, deploy, and incident tips.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Start / Stop</h2>
  <div class="callout">
    <pre>cd /opt/quirk/quirk-closedai/deploy
docker compose up -d     # start
docker compose ps        # status
docker compose logs -f   # tail logs
docker compose down      # stop</pre>
  </div>

  <h2>Checks</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Caddy cert valid; 200 on <code>/.well-known</code> ACME paths.</li>
    <li>Gateway health; Twilio WebSocket connects.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Common incidents</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>DNS mispointing → verify A-record & public IP.</li>
    <li>TLS fail → check CAA, firewall 80/443, time skew.</li>
    <li>Media path fail → verify TwiML Bin URL + logs.</li>
  </ul>

